description: , Colorful Photo Wooden Jigsaw Puzzle - 180 Pieces, finished size 10.5” x 8”, of Antonio Gaudi's masterpiece in Barcelona.
THE PERFECT GIFT FOR PUZZLE DOERS - Wooden Jigsaw Puzzles make the perfect gift for Valentine's Day, Christmas, Hanukkah, Mother’s Day, Father’s Day, Birthday, Anniversary and Retirement.

EVERY LASER CUT NAUTILUS WOODEN JIGSAW PUZZLE is manufactured in the U.S.A. from 4 mm Finnish Birch Plywood that has been harvested from sustainably managed forests. The puzzles are cut in the classic Victorian puzzle style and feature creative, intricate pieces, and many shaped figural whimsy pieces, that are designed to match the theme, style and art of the puzzle. The cutting technique guarantees that every piece is a little work of art. Wooden Puzzles do not interlock in the same way as cardboard puzzles, so there is a different tactile experience in putting the puzzle together, making the puzzle more challenging to work, but incredibly entertaining.

This is a 180 pieces random Victorian cut full color jigsaw puzzle with unique pieces. Keep it for yourself or give it to a friend or family member as a gift. Wooden puzzles are designed to be collectible and the sturdy wooden construction allows them to be handed down as heirlooms from generation to generation. Regardless of your choice, anyone will enjoy the stunning art caught on this captivating puzzle. Perfect for teens, adults, men and women, this design will appeal to a wide range of puzzlers.

Wooden Jigsaw Puzzles are a simple pastimes for all ages. They provide a stress-free, yet challenging and entertaining task that can be enjoyed in front of the fire or on the porch at the end of a long day.
Wooden puzzles are also great at keeping your mind sharp and connected as you age. They are the perfect form of stress free artful mind game, designed to challenge you and make you think.
